title: Owen's Last Day Before Leaving Barstool Sports - Full Episode
description:
Owen Roeder recounts his time at Barstool Sports and admits he's always been a huge KFC Radio listener. He also tells the story of how he recently got thrown off a plane, recounts the best days of childhood, smoking pretzels, and much more. Dave App: Download the Dave app from the App store


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
